<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        * {
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
            height: auto;
            color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .parallax {
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background: url('/images/NN.png') no-repeat;
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-attachment: fixed;
        }

        .parallax img {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .parallax img#tree-left {
            position: absolute;
            /* Fix: Added position property */
            transform: translateX(-5px);
        }

        .parallax img#tree-right {
            position: absolute;
            /* Fix: Added position property */
            transform: translateX(5px);
        }

        .parallax img#gate-left {
            position: absolute;
            /* Fix: Added position property */
            transform: translateX(-332px);
        }

        .parallax img#gate-right {
            position: absolute;
            /* Fix: Added position property */
            transform: translateX(332px);
        }

        #text {
            position: relative;
            bottom: 140px;
            /* Fix: Added position property */
            font-size: 5em;
            color: #fff;
            text-shadow: 2px 4px 5px #f9f9f9;
        }

        .sec {
            position: relative;
            background-color: #020912;
            padding: 30px 100px;
            height: 90vh;
        }

        .sec h2 {
            font-size: 3em;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .sec p {
            font-size: 1.6em;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 300;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .sec p+p {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <section class="parallax">
        <h2 id="text">About Us</h2>
        <img src="\images\tree-left.png" id="tree-left">
        <img src="\images\tree-right.png" id="tree-right">
        <img src="\images\gate-left.png" id="gate-left">
        <img src="\images\gate-right.png" id="gate-right">
        <img src="\images\grass.png" id="grass">
    </section>
    <section class="sec">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <h2 style="position: relative;bottom:79px;left:80vh;">Established since 2024</h2>
        <center><strong>Who We Are</strong></center>
        <p>Our legacy traces back to a time when elegance, refinement, and opulence were not mere aspirations—they were
            a way of life. We understand that true luxury transcends the material; it resides in the stories whispered
            by well-worn leather seats, the timeless hum of a finely tuned engine, and the allure of a classic
            silhouette against the setting sun.</p>
        <p>Our mission is simple: to transform your automotive desires into tangible experiences. Whether you seek the
            dignified grace of a vintage Rolls-Royce or the cutting-edge performance of a modern Bentley, Astra is your
            gateway to a world where every drive is an ode to sophistication. We believe that owning a luxury car isn’t
            just about status; it’s about embracing a heritage—a lineage that whispers secrets of prosperity and taste.
        </p>
        <p>Join us on this journey—a pilgrimage for those who appreciate the symphony of a finely tuned engine, the
            aroma of aged leather, and the thrill of a winding road. At Astra, we don’t just sell cars; we orchestrate
            legacies. Welcome to a world where old money meets modern aspiration, and where every drive is a nod to the
            past, a salute to the present, and a promise to the future.</p>
    </section>

    <script src="/script.js"></script>
</body>


</html>